cast.original_title: The Last Kingdom: Seven Kings Must Die
cast.overview: In the wake of King Edward's death, Uhtred of Bebbanburg and his comrades adventure across a fractured kingdom in the hopes of uniting England at last.
cast.title: The Last Kingdom: Seven Kings Must Die

details.biography: Jacob Dudman (born 22 August 1997) is an English actor, voice over artist and filmmaker. He is known for his roles in Netflix's The Last Kingdom, Medici, The Stranger, HBO's Primal, The Choral, FATE:The Winx Saga and as the titular character in the Doctor Who audio range.
details.name: Jacob Dudman
